Name: _______________________________  Class: _________________________

Engineering Criteria Assignment

Based on the following scenario, write a series of criteria and constraints that you think would help produce the best 
solution to the following problem. 

A local business, a supermarket (grocery store,) has a problem. Their new products come in boxes of different sizes, making them difficult to store. 

They want you, and your engineering design firm, to create a storage solution for their boxes over the next three months.


